<template>
    <el-row>
  <el-col :sm="12" :lg="6">
    <el-result icon="success" :title=page.leftBuRu subTitle="剩余哺乳假">
      <template slot="extra">
        <el-button type="primary" size="medium">返回</el-button>
      </template>
    </el-result>
  </el-col>
  <el-col :sm="12" :lg="6">
    <el-result icon="warning" title="警告提示" subTitle="请根据提示进行操作">
      <template slot="extra">
        <el-button type="primary" size="medium">返回</el-button>
      </template>
    </el-result>
  </el-col>
  <el-col :sm="12" :lg="6">
    <el-result icon="error" title="错误提示" subTitle="请根据提示进行操作">
      <template slot="extra">
        <el-button type="primary" size="medium">返回</el-button>
      </template>
    </el-result>
  </el-col>
  <el-col :sm="12" :lg="6">
    <el-result icon="info" title="信息提示" subTitle="请根据提示进行操作">
      <template slot="extra">
        <el-button type="primary" size="medium">返回</el-button>
      </template>
    </el-result>
  </el-col>
</el-row>
</template>
<script>
export default {
    data(){
        return{
            page:[]
        }
    },
    created() {
        this.loaddata();
    },
    methods: {
        loaddata() {
            var empId = window.sessionStorage.getItem('empId');
            this.$http.get('/getLeftTimeById/'+empId).then(res => {
                console.log(res.data);
                this.page = res.data;
            });
        }
    },
}
</script>
